reviewText: I made a mistake ordering this movie about a girl who gets pregnant by mistake.  The movie made me feel bad, and was a waste of $20.00.  Its headed for the garbage.  What a dumb "played out" old story.  I feel I was Mislead by Mr. Skin who said the movie was STORMY, and to put a "weather watch" on it.  I guess I don't know what that means.
